Write two to three sentences on why Django is so popular among web developers.

Django is popular because it includes many useful features right from the start, such as routing, a database
layer, an admin panel, and user authentication. This makes it faster to build web applications without setting
everything up yourself. It is also written in Python, which is easy to read, and it has a large community that
provides helpful support and many add-on tools.


